reply_text:
@youraveragefortniteogre121A story with the most predictable script, awful dialogue, lines that make you roll your eyes because they’re so corny or you’ve heard them a million times.
I especially liked the moment when one of the characters said “this can’t be” or smth when they see two killers :)))) why? It was so forced and meant to make us go “oooh, so there are two” when in fact the movie doesn’t focus on making us care.
At this point there are so many slashers in this world to make it easy to identify a bad one and my god, this is one of them.
